Peng Pai journalist Li Jiawei and her doctor a few days ago watched the sunset of 87-year-old people continue to improve, recently negative nucleic acid testing, CT signs of lung lesions improved.
此前报道《“今日最佳照片”里的医生，我们找到了》3月12日，澎湃新闻记者从上海中山医院支援湖北医疗队获悉这一消息。
We found the doctor who had previously reported on "Today's Best Picture." On March 12, Peng Pai journalists from the Zhongshan Hospital in Shanghai supported the Hubei Medical Team to learn the news.
医疗队队员刘凯医生称，老先生各方面情况均已显著转好，近期医护人员在加强老先生的康复锻炼，预计一周左右老人就出院了。
Dr Liu Kai, a member of the medical team, said that the situation of the old man had improved markedly. Recently, medical staff were strengthening the rehabilitation of the old man and he was expected to leave the hospital in about a week.
